doctype html
html(lang="en")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    meta(name="viewport", content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0")
    title 注册账户
    style.
      .highlight {
        background-color: yellow;
        color: black;
        padding: 2px 5px;
        border-radius: 3px;
      }
      .indent {
        padding-left: 12px;
      }
  body
    p #{email},
    p.indent Hello！
    p.indent 您好！
    p.indent Please fill in the following captcha within #{validLifeTime} minutes:
      span.highlight #{num}
    p.indent 请在 #{validLifeTime} 分钟内填写如下验证码：
      span.highlight #{num}
    p.indent Please do not reply to this email as it is sent from an unmanned mailbox.
    p.indent 请不要回复此电子邮件，因为它是无人值守的邮箱发送的。